description:
Show them you care with a gorgeous bottle of Moët & Chandon bubbly paired with delicious gourmet treats. Filled with exquisite artisan gourmet food, including a selection of some of Australia's finest gourmet producers, this is the ultimate gift hamper for every occasion.

Whether you need to say 'I love you', 'well done', or 'congratulations', this hamper will speak volumes. Of course, the true star of this gourmet gift hamper is the exquisite bottle of Moët & Chandon. It's the perfect bubbly when celebrations are in order.

To accompany one of the world's finest bottles of champagne, it's important to select only the world's finest fare to enjoy alongside. Both sweet and savoury treats have been included so everyone's tastebuds will be impressed. So, what are you waiting for? With FREE delivery over $99 you can't go past our gourmet gift hampers to impress.

Please Note: Due to seasonal variations and exclusivity of our stock, items in hampers are occasionally substituted for products of the same or higher value and quality.
name: The Hamper Emporium 1EA
